{"tid":2186089,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★外媒：中國1960年代嬰兒潮步入退休 佔目前人口約20% 恐對中國產生急劇轉變。","createTime":"2020-09-02T16:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T17:16:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c2618bf716d1eab7c6992f8ec66ab0fc19668e83","tid":2186089,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:30:09.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，中國內地於1960年代有一大規模嬰兒潮，當時約有2.45億人出生，佔目前中國總人口約20%，是中國歷史上出生人口最多、對後來經濟影響最大的主力嬰兒潮。瑞士信貸(Credit Suisse)發布最新報告估計，這一代嬰兒潮將在未來幾年退休，恐對中國產生急劇轉變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200902/bkn-20200902142741804-0902_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200902%2Fbkn-20200902142741804-0902_00842_001.html&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hd9ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=e36e333a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200902/bkn-20200902142741804-0902_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a831bd6f23b0017a15f25157ee84e60fdcca148b","tid":2186089,"uid":116910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<br />\n120歲命<br />\n60 歲都係中年姐"},{"pid":"2554c6130222a2f306514408d3782cb4dfa95c6d","tid":2186089,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"驚西咩，拜登is coming<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySYFF71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySYFF71.jpg&h=aa7b994c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8167cfb2464807c7bab6e96df3c31e358db4d4c","tid":2186089,"uid":230146,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實醒目嘅就將退休年齡延長至65/70，<br />\n理論上可以延續個經濟發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n55歲退休，痴撚線食足至少二十年退休金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔覺得個社會頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/